   <body>
      <context>
         <p>The <uicontrol>Budget Estimate Revision</uicontrol> form tracks only the updates made to the budget estimate. The  approved  budget is revised to add, modify, or deleted.</p>
         <p>The budget estimate revisions are received through integration with EBS. </p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>In the module menu, click <uicontrol>Projects</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>PROJECTS</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the list page, double-click the required project.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the navigation pane, expand the project folder, and expand <uicontrol>Budget Management</uicontrol>, and then click <uicontrol>Budget Estimate Revision</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATE REVISION</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the list page, select the appropriate record, and then click <uicontrol>View</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATE REVISION DETAILS</uicontrol> page is displayed.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <title>Budget Estimate Revision Details Page</title>
                  <image href="../../../Icons/Screenshots_Icons/Bdgt_EstmteRevDetails.jpg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Provide the required information in the fields, as described in the following table.</p>
            <p>
               <table colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                  <tgroup cols="2">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="30%"/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="70%"/>
                     <thead>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Field Name</entry>
                           <entry>Description</entry>
                        </row>
                     </thead>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Budget Estimate Rev ID</entry>
                           <entry>An identification number for the budget estimate revision.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Budget Estimate Rev Name</entry>
                           <entry>The name of the revised budget estimate.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Budget Estimate ID</entry>
                           <entry>The code of the approved budget estimate for which the revision is  created.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Budget Estimate Name</entry>
                           <entry>The name of the approved budget estimate for which the revision is  created.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>PWA Project Number</entry>
                           <entry>The identification number of the associated project.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Project Name</entry>
                           <entry>The name of the associated project.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Budget Estimate Type</entry>
                           <entry>The budget estimate type of the approved budget estimate for which the revision is  created.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Measurement System</entry>
                           <entry>The measurement system used in the approved budget estimate.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Standard Item List</entry>
                           <entry>This field is blank.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Description</entry>
                           <entry>The description of the budget estimate revision.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Estimate Total in $</entry>
                           <entry>A value is displayed based on the EBS added, deleted, or modified in  the <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATE REVISION ITEMS</uicontrol> tab.</entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To view the details of EBS, click the <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATE REVISION ITEMS</uicontrol> tab.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <title>Budget Estimate Revision Items Page</title>
                  <image href="../../../Icons/Screenshots_Icons/Bdgt_EstmteRevItems.jpg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATE REVISION ITEMS</uicontrol> page displays the following non-editable fields:<table colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                  <tgroup cols="2">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="30%"/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="70%"/>
                     <thead>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Column Name</entry>
                           <entry>Description</entry>
                        </row>
                     </thead>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Task Number</entry>
                           <entry>The task number  as received from EBS.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Line Number</entry>
                           <entry>The line number of the task as received from EBS.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Task Name</entry>
                           <entry>The name of the task as received from EBS.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Unit</entry>
                           <entry>The unit of measure assigned for the task.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Quantity</entry>
                           <entry>The quantity is defaulted to 1.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Unit Price in $</entry>
                           <entry>The unit price for the task as received from EBS.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Fund Rule</entry>
                           <entry>This field is blank.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Amount in $</entry>
                           <entry>It is auto-calculated as: Quantity * Unit Price.</entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
